![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9e789a18-c43c-4735-bfc5-27e9db646099/FB_IMG_1717978724256.jpg)

Sexyy Red welcomes everyone to NXT Battleground!

Then twerks.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/38fab272-9106-4ebe-94b4-0241b484d289/received_1206618213682529.jpeg)

*   ## **_NXT NORTH AMERICAN WOMENS CHAMPIONSHIP LADDER MATCH: KALANI JORDAN DEF. JAIDA PARKER, MICHIN, SOL RUCA, FALLON HENLY_**
    

This was about as good as a ladder match full of 6 green horns could be. Lash Legend took the biggest spot as they tossed her through a ladder on the outside.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d16119f3-5f09-47d1-aad9-a3a15f68fb9a/received_1122188672229287.jpeg)

*   ## **_NXT TAG TEAM CHAMPIONSHIPS: AXOM AND NATHAN FRAIZER(c) DEF. GOOD BROTHERS_**
    

As much as I am bored with the Good Brothers, they’ve got their working boots on here. Very good match here. Frazier and AXIOM continue a great reign.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ad337f6e-8107-463d-8c30-d97bc4087956/received_2603188790041456.jpeg)

*   ## **_NXT UNDERGROUND: LOLA VICE DEF. SHAYNA BASZLER_** BY TKO
    

After a sea of promos and commercials as they set this match up. We finally get under way.

This is probably the Underground match with the most accurate MMA simulation moves and spots. Whether it was good or not will depend on your ability to stomach simulated MMA spots.

I personally found them very well done, for the most part.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/de8621b1-5b37-4d40-b7e1-71c3912c1156/received_392496659821495.jpeg)

*   ## **_NXT NORTH AMERICAN CHAMPIONSHIP: OBA FEMI DEF. WES LEE AND JOE COFFEY_**
    

Good grief, what a match!!

Quick paced, hard hitting match that saw Oba Femi throwing his opponents around like Rag Dolls before Gallus got involved. Oba Femi overcame all obstacles to retain here.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/15b1013e-4c1b-467a-84d3-4d496b17b171/received_441458031929535.jpeg)

*   ## **_NXT WOMENS CHAMPIONSHIP: ROXANNE PEREZ DEF. TNA KNOCKOUTS CHAMPION JORDYNNE GRACE_**
    

Roxanne Perez squeaks out a win over Jordynne Grace in a fantastic match after some shenanigans outside the ring involving Tatum Paxley and Ash By Elegance (yup, Dana Brooke)

At one point, one of Jordynne's earrings got yanked out of her ear and lodged into Roxanne's THIGH!

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/42da10b8-927e-44d2-bb57-1e6930be0bce/received_2770830659742266.jpeg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e7b3f3fe-4314-47c9-85da-0186edd1f0ad/received_745373437802982.jpeg)

*   ## **_NXT CHAMPIONSHIP: TRICK WILLIAMS DEF. ETHAN PAGE_**
    

Ethan Page's Ego got the better of him. Frustrated, he argues with the official and eats a Trick Shot for his hubris!

Trick Williams retains his NXT Championship!

He then celebrates with Sexyy Red as NXT goes off the air.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d2b10f74-be04-4769-8571-07ef2ff2e78d/received_454993497248310.jpeg)